This is the Readme file for SMPReaderUSB host program.

  README .............. The file you are currently reading.

  smpusb.c ............ Main host code
  opendevice.c ........ common functions for USB device opening
  opendevice.h ........ common functions for USB device opening
  smpusb.vcproj ....... Microsoft Visual C project file
  smpusb.sln .......... Microsoft Visual solution file
  stdafx.cpp .......... precompiled header file
  stdafx.h ............ precompiled header file
  targetver.h ......... Windows version definition 
  

PREREQUISITES
=============

Host side program are compiled with Microsoft Visual Studio C/C++ for Windows platform.

Project depend on libusb. Libusb is available from

http://libusb.sourceforge.net/ for Unix and
http://libusb-win32.sourceforge.net/ for Windows.

COMPILATION
===========

1. Install libusb-win32
2. Open smpusb.vcproj project in Visual Studio, open project "Properties"
3. Choose "C/C++", modify "Additional Include Directories" to point to 
   <Libusb-Win32-install-dir>/include
4. Press OK
5. Delete "libusb.lib" form solution explorer tree
6. Press left mouse button at project and choose "Add"->"Existing Item",
   than choose <Libusb-Win32-install-dir>/lib/msvc/libusb.lib

